@page "/fleet"

<PageTitle>Colletion</PageTitle>

<div class="container-fluid p-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <h2 class="fs-1 text-uppercase">Browse our collection</h2>
            <h4 class="pt-5">See anything you like?</h4>
            <h6>Use the contact form below and specify what model you are intersted in renting.</h6>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid p-5">
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-xl-4 g-4">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-1.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Porche 911 T">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Porche 911 S</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Introduced in September 1964 by Porsche AG of Stuttgart, this rear-engined sports car boasts a rear-mounted flat-six engine and a torsion bar suspension.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1989</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. AND243</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-2.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Ford Model T Touring">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Ford Model T Touring</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">The Ford Model T, manufactured by the Ford Motor Company from 1908 to 1927, is widely recognized as the pioneering mass-affordable automobile.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1925</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. AWL853</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-3.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Duesenberg Model J">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Duesenberg Model J</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Launched in 1928 and created to challenge luxury car titans. Available with a supercharger after 1932 and was sold until Duesenberg Motors Cp's 1937 bankruptcy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1933</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. PQZ552</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-4.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Buick Series 90 Convertible">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Buick Series 90 Convertible</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Built on Buick's largest chassis and powered by Buick's largest straight-eight, convertible coupes were the only 1931 open-bodied Buicks that received Fisher bodies.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1931</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. VUQ516</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-5.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Chevrolet Bel Air">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Chevrolet Bel Air</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Produced from 1950 to 1981 as a two-door hardtop designation and evolved into a premium trim level in 1953. U.S. production ended in 1975, continuing in Canada until 1981.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1954</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. IEN716</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-car-6.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Chevrolet Impala">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Chevrolet Impala</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Produced from 1958 to 1985, and from 2000 to 2020. Known as Chevrolet's flagship full-size car. It enjoyed significant popularity, ranking among the top-selling U.S. automobiles.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1970</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. ENN712</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-mc-1.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="Porsche 930">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Lossa Yamaha SR 500</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">Developed to be "easy to use," its design was revised for easier starting after an ankle injury of Yamaha's Technical Director, leading to a decompression lever system.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1978</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. MBU852</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 border-dark">
                <img src="images/fleet-mc-2.jpg" class="card-img-top border-bottom border-dark" alt="1969 Benelli 350cc Grand Prix Racing Motorcycle">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h6 class="card-title">Benelli 350cc</h6>
                    <p class="card-text">350cc was sold through Montgomery Ward. The advent of competition led to Benelli products use of single cylinder pushrod design.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <small class="small-card-text">Prod. in 1969</small><small class="small-card-text"># Reg No. WCK661</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid p-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <h4 class="pt-5 text">Fill in the form below</h4>
            <h6>Please provide the registration number of the vehicle you are interested in, along with your contact information, and we will promptly respond to your inquiry.</h6>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid p-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <form>
                <div>
                    <label for="regNumber" class="form-label">Registration Number:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="regNumber" name="regNumber" class="form-control placeholder-form-text" placeholder="ABC123">
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3">
                    <label for="phoneNumber" class="form-label">Phone Number:</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phoneNumber" name="phoneNumber" class="form-control placeholder-form-text" placeholder="+0">
                </div>
                <div class="mt-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">E-mail:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control placeholder-form-text" placeholder="email@email.com" aria-describedby="emailHelp">
                    <div id="emailHelp" class="form-text">We will never share your email with anyone else.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="my-3 form-check">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="termsCheckbox" name="terms">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="termsCheckbox">I agree to the <a href="placeholder">terms</a> of service.</label>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
